ging field operations and using data to drive conversations and decisions.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat You’ll Do\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cul data-list-tree=\"true\" data-indent=\"0\" data-border=\"0\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLead on-ground captain acquisition operations across the UAE\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBuild and maintain strong working relationships with 3PL partners (vendors) and logistics suppliers\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupport vendors in improving their recruitment, onboarding, and captain readiness processes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAlign captain supply with Careem’s growth plans and ensure partners consistently meet their commitments\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTrack, monitor, and enforce supply fulfillment targets (e.g., ensuring committed captain numbers are onboarded on time)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eActively work with partners to improve performance, solve operational bottlenecks, and raise quality standards\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDistribute captain uniforms/swag and coordinate onboarding and training initiatives\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eServe as the primary point of contact for resolving day-to-day operational issues with suppliers and captains\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaintain structured documentation and reporting on acquisition progress, partner performance, and overall supply health\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eManage and guide the team to ensure clear direction, accountability, and high-quality execution\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse data and performance metrics to identify gaps, drive corrective actions, and support decision-making\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat You’ll Need\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cul data-list-tree=\"true\" data-indent=\"0\" data-border=\"0\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e3–5 years of experience in acquisition, logistics, vendor management, or operations in a fast-paced environment (e.g., food tech, q-commerce, mobility)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProven experience working closely with external partners or suppliers and managing on-ground operations\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStrong communication and relationship-building skills, with the ability to influence partners\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eComfortable working with data: able to track metrics, interpret performance trends, and use numbers to guide actions and discussions\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIntermediate Excel skills required; ability to work with reports and performance trackers is essential\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnalytical mindset with a habit of using data to identify issues and opportunities\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProficiency in Hindi or Urdu preferred; Arabic is a plus but not mandatory\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStrong ownership mindset with the ability to operate independently and thrive in a fast-changing environment\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat We’ll Provide You\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWe offer colleagues the opportunity to drive real impact in the region while learning and growing in a high-ownership environment. As a full-time Careem colleague, you will be able to:\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cul data-list-tree=\"true\" data-indent=\"0\" data-border=\"0\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork and learn from talented, driven colleagues across functions\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eContribute to a mission-driven organization focused on building reliable everyday services\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExplore new opportunities to learn and grow every day\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork in a hybrid setup (4 days in office, 1 day from home) and remotely from any country for up to 30 days a year, with unlimited vacation days\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAccess healthcare benefits and fitness reimbursements for activities including gym memberships, health clubs, and training classes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","introduction":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eCareem is building the Everything App for the greater Middle East — making it easy to move around, order food and groceries, manage payments, and more. Our purpose is simple: to simplify and improve people’s lives and build an awesome organisation that inspires.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eSince 2012, Careem has enabled earnings for over 2.5 million Captains, simplified the lives of more than 70 million customers, and built a platform where the region’s best talent and entrepreneurs thrive. We operate in 70+ cities across 10 countries, from Morocco to Pakistan.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-stringify-type=\"bold\"\u003e\u003cem data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003eWe’re now entering our next chapter — one powered by AI. We’re looking for AI talent: curious problem-solvers who know how to apply AI to build tools, automate workflows, and create real impact. Whether it’s streamlining operations, enhancing customer experience, or reimagining internal systems — we want people who can make Careem work smarter and move faster.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","conclusion":"","enable_eeoc":false,"job_post_location":"Dubai, United Arab Emirates","public_url":"https://boards.greenhouse.io/careem/jobs/8245588002?gh_jid=8245588002","company_name":"Careem","confirmation_message":"\u003cp\u003eWe are thrilled that you are interested to be part of Careem!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWe have received your application and one of our Recruiters will review it. Due to the volume of applications, we are unable to give a response to all applications, and prioritize the ones that meet the role requirements. Check out our careers page for the role that may be the best match for your experience - www.careem.com/careers\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTalent Acquisition | Careem\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","pay_ranges":[],"published_at":"2025-11-11T04:20:40-05:00","employment":"hidden","fingerprint":"21aead92285f12fa3960ff33fd598280b1b0d123","redirect_to":null,"is_featured":false,"ai_disclaimer":null,"include_ai_disclaimer":false,"apply_with_seek":null,"show_quick_apply_cta":true,"ai_opt_out_request_url":"http://app2.greenhouse.io/ai_opt_out_request/job_post/8245588002/ai_opt_out","education_config":{"id":8154384002,"school_name":"hidden","degree":"hidden","discipline":"hidden","start_month":"hidden","start_year":"hidden","end_month":"hidden","end_year":"hidden"},"questions":[{"required":true,"label":"First Name","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"first_name","type":"input_text"}]},{"required":true,"label":"Last Name","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"last_name","type":"input_text"}]},{"required":true,"label":"Email","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"email","type":"input_text"}]},{"required":true,"label":"Phone","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"phone","type":"input_text"}]},{"required":true,"label":"Candidate Location","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"candidate_location","type":"input_text"}]},{"required":true,"label":"Resume/CV","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"resume","type":"input_file","allowed_filetypes":["pdf","doc","docx","txt","rtf"]},{"name":"resume_text","type":"textarea"}]},{"required":false,"label":"Cover Letter","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"cover_letter","type":"input_file","allowed_filetypes":["pdf","doc","docx","txt","rtf"]},{"name":"cover_letter_text","type":"textarea"}]},{"required":true,"label":"Current Employer","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"question_33793262002","type":"input_text"}],"multi_select_style":"checkbox"},{"required":true,"label":"Current Job