_apply":false,"display_departments":true,"display_search_bar":true,"display_new_jobs_tag":true,"display_number_of_open_jobs":true,"display_footer":true,"candidate_portal_enabled":true,"application_tracking_enabled":false,"seek_id":"","enable_recruitics":true,"appcast_tracking_code":null,"google_drive_enabled":true,"enable_dropbox":true,"allow_external_notifications":true,"display_job_trust_profiles":false,"grayscale_ai_bot_enabled":false,"grayscale_ai_bot_access_token":null},"urlToken":"careem","embedded":false,"isJobPost":true},"routes/$url_token_.jobs_.$job_post_id":{"jobPost":{"post_type":"job_post","language":"en","title":"Captain Experience Associate","hiring_plan_id":6352696002,"content":"\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAbout the role\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\nAs a\u0026nbsp;\u003cstrong\u003eCaptain Experience Associate\u003c/strong\u003e, your mission is to elevate the gold standard of our service. You will own the end-to-end quality of the Captain journey, using data-driven insights, targeted marketing, and strategic partnerships to ensure every Captain delivers a seamless, high-quality experience to our customers.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat you'll do\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStandards Governance:\u003c/strong\u003e Define and monitor the \"Perfect Order\" metrics, focusing on reducing delays, returns, and defect rates.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePerformance Intervention:\u003c/strong\u003e Identify low-performing outliers and develop improvement plans, training interventions, or corrective workflows to maintain fleet quality.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRoot Cause Analysis:\u003c/strong\u003e Manage the lifecycle of captain-related tickets, identifying systemic issues and coordinating with tech/ops teams for long-term fixes.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeedback Loops:\u003c/strong\u003e Conduct regular quality audits and sentiment surveys to ensure the \"Captain Voice\" is used to improve operational processes.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBehavioral Campaigns:\u003c/strong\u003e Plan and execute a marketing calendar specifically designed to nudge positive behaviors\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEducational Content:\u003c/strong\u003e Collaborate with central marketing to produce high-quality training materials, videos, and guides that simplify complex operational procedures and improve service delivery.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCommunity Recognition:\u003c/strong\u003e Organize events and appreciation programs that celebrate top-tier performers, reinforcing a culture of excellence.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eValue-Added Incentives:\u003c/strong\u003e Identify and onboard partners who provide benefits that specifically help Captains maintain high standards (e.g., discounted vehicle maintenance, data plans, or safety gear).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRelationship Management:\u003c/strong\u003e Manage the partnership roadmap to ensure all perks are aligned with our quality goals and provide genuine value to the fleet.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCross-Functional Bridge:\u003c/strong\u003e Serve as the primary link between the fleet and the internal operations team to ensure smooth, day-to-day execution of orders.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat you'll need\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e2–3 years of professional experience.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Quality Obsessive:\u003c/strong\u003e You have high standards and a sharp eye for the details that make or break a customer experience.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Data Interpreter:\u003c/strong\u003e You are comfortable with spreadsheets and can translate raw metrics into an action plan.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Clear Communicator:\u003c/strong\u003e You can break down complex operational rules into simple, catchy, and persuasive marketing content.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Process Optimizer:\u003c/strong\u003e You aren't just looking to fix a problem once; you want to fix the system that caused it.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we’ll provide you\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe offer colleagues the opportunity to drive impact in the region while they learn and grow. As a full time Careem colleague, you will be able to:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork and learn from great minds by joining a community of inspiring colleagues.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePut your passion to work in a purposeful organisation dedicated to creating impact in a region with a lot of untapped potential.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExplore new opportunities to learn and grow every day.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork 4 days a week in office \u0026amp; 1 day from home, and remotely from any country in the world for 30 days a year with unlimited vacation days per year. (If you are in an individual contributor role in tech, you will have 2 office days a week and 3 to work from home.)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAccess to healthcare benefits and fitness reimbursements for health activities including gym, health club, and training classes.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","introduction":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eCareem is building the Everything App for the greater Middle East — making it easy to move around, order food and groceries, manage payments, and more. Our purpose is simple: to simplify and improve people’s lives and build an awesome organisation that inspires.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eSince 2012, Careem has enabled earnings for over 2.5 million Captains, simplified the lives of more than 70 million customers, and built a platform where the region’s best talent and entrepreneurs thrive. We operate in 70+ cities across 10 countries, from Morocco to Pakistan.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-stringify-type=\"bold\"\u003e\u003cem data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003eWe’re now entering our next chapter — one powered by AI. We’re looking for AI talent: curious problem-solvers who know how to apply AI to build tools, automate workflows, and create real impact. Whether it’s streamlining operations, enhancing customer experience, or reimagining internal systems — we want people who can make Careem work smarter and move faster.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","conclusion":"","enable_eeoc":false,"job_post_location":"Amman, Jordan","public_url":"https://boards.greenhouse.io/careem/jobs/8397974002?gh_jid=8397974002","company_name":"Careem","confirmation_message":"\u003cp\u003eWe are thrilled that you are interested to be part of Careem!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWe have received your application and one of our Recruiters will review it. Due to the volume of applications, we are unable to give a response to all applications, and prioritize the ones that meet the role requirements. Check out our careers page for the role that may be the best match for your experience - www.careem.com/careers\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTalent Acquisition | Careem\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","pay_ranges":[],"published_at":"2026-02-26T07:03:28-05:00","employment":"hidden","fingerprint":"7fd9ac678a4aa32848bc538308e6524dd733c7cc","redirect_to":null,"is_featured":false,"a