n the P\u0026amp;L for categories and assortment strategy\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003eDevelop strategic sourcing strategies, lead supplier negotiations and onboarding, ensuring alignment with Careem’s commercial requirements and expectations\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003eWork closely with supply chain and demand planning teams to maintain high availability and optimized inventory levels\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003ePartner with marketing and product teams to drive visibility, adoption and conversion of SKUs\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003eMonitor category performance, customer feedback, and market trends to refine strategies\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003eCollaborate with legal, finance, and compliance to ensure all products meet regulatory standards\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"p-rich_text_section\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-stringify-type=\"bold\"\u003eWhat you’ll need\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet p-rich_text_list--nested\" data-stringify-type=\"unordered-list\" data-list-tree=\"true\" data-indent=\"0\" data-border=\"0\"\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003e5–8 years of experience in category management, merchandising, procurement or strategic sourcing — ideally in grocery retail or FMCG\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003eProven track record of owning commercial KPIs and delivering on margin and growth targets\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003eStrong negotiation skills and experience managing supplier relationships\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003eAnalytical mindset with comfort in Excel and data tools to drive decisions - Entrepreneurial drive, ownership mindset, and bias for action\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\"\u003eExcellent cross-functional collaboration and communication skills\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we’ll provide you\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe offer colleagues the opportunity to drive impact in the region while they learn and grow. As a full time Careem colleague, you will be able to:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork and learn from great minds by joining a community of inspiring colleagues.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePut your passion to work in a purposeful organisation dedicated to creating impact in a region with a lot of untapped potential.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExplore new opportunities to learn and grow every day.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork 4 days a week in office \u0026amp; 1 day from home, and remotely from any country in the world for 30 days a year with unlimited vacation days per year. (If you are in an individual contributor role in tech, you will have 2 office days a week and 3 to work from home.)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAccess to healthcare benefits and fitness reimbursements for health activities including gym, health club, and training classes.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","introduction":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eCareem is building the Everything App for the greater Middle East — making it easy to move around, order food and groceries, manage payments, and more. Our purpose is simple: to simplify and improve people’s lives and build an awesome organisation that inspires.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eSince 2012, Careem has enabled earnings for over 2.5 million Captains, simplified the lives of more than 70 million customers, and built a platform where the region’s best talent and entrepreneurs thrive. We operate in 70+ cities across 10 countries, from Morocco to Pakistan.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-stringify-type=\"bold\"\u003e\u003cem data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003eWe’re now entering our next chapter — one powered by AI. We’re looking for AI talent: curious problem-solvers who know how to apply AI to build tools, automate workflows, and create real impact. Whether it’s streamlining operations, enhancing customer experience, or reimagining internal systems — we want people who can make Careem work smarter and move faster.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","conclusion":"","enable_eeoc":false,"job_post_location":"Riyadh, Saudi Arabia","public_url":"https://boards.greenhouse.io/careem/jobs/8358329002?gh_jid=8358329002","company_name":"Careem","confirmation_message":"\u003cp\u003eWe are thrilled that you are interested to be part of Careem!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWe have received your application and one of our Recruiters will review it. Due to the volume of applications, we are unable to give a response to all applications, and prioritize the ones that meet the role requirements. Check out our careers page for the role that may be the best match for your experience - www.careem.com/careers\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTalent Acquisition | Careem\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","pay_ranges":[],"published_at":"2026-01-27T09:01:19-05:00","employment":"hidden","fingerprint":"8f5793f4c017a3fb09a05653fbe2e4735f9ead00","redirect_to":null,"is_featured":false,"ai_disclaimer":null,"include_ai_disclaimer":false,"apply_with_seek":null,"show_quick_apply_cta":true,"ai_opt_out_request_url":"h