on\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eOur Category teams manage thousands of SKUs. Build an AI prototype that analyzes sales, margin, and stock data to recommend which SKUs to keep, replace, or promote. Show how automation can improve profitability.\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e2. The Future of Merchandising\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eImagine Category Management powered entirely by AI. Build or demo a tool that transforms how categories are managed \u0026mdash; from dynamic pricing to automated vendor negotiations.\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e3. Smart Assortment Prompt\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eDesign a ChatGPT prompt that recommends the right assortment mix based on inputs like sales trends, supplier performance, and customer preferences.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow it works:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e- Use any public or dummy data (e.g. Kaggle, data.gov, or self-created), if required. Avoid using any confidential information.\u003cbr\u003e- You can use free tools like ChatGPT, Google Colab, Google Sheets + App Script, Streamlit, or Hugging Face. Expect to spend around 30\u0026ndash;60 minutes on it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSubmit:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e- A public link, document, or screenshots of your prototype or prompt\u003cbr\u003e- A public dataset link (if relevant)\u003cbr\u003e- A short 100-word summary of your idea and approach\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003c!--EndFragment--\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","fields":[{"name":"question_34850106002","type":"input_file","allowed_filetypes":["pdf","doc","docx","txt","rtf"]}],"multi_select_style":"checkbox"},{"required":true,"label":"Did you attempt the previous question?","description":null,"fields":[{"name":"question_34850107002","type":"multi_value_single_select","values":[{"value":219231191002,"label":"No I did not attempt it"},{"value":219231192002,"label":"Yes - Option 1"},{"value":219231193002,"labe